				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Bi%E1%BB%87t-%C4%90%E1%BB%95ng-%C4%90%C4%A9nh/poem-MVXURB9dNzgngfukwqcFjg">Biệt Đổng Đĩnh - 別董頲</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%B4i-Th%E1%BB%B1/C%E1%BB%ADu-nh%E1%BA%ADt-%C4%91%C4%83ng-V%E1%BB%8Dng-Ti%C3%AAn-%C4%91%C3%A0i-tr%C3%ACnh-L%C6%B0u-Minh-Ph%E1%BB%A7-Dung/poem-Jqxkds7pHuteyy5u98H4ow">Cửu nhật đăng Vọng Tiên đài, trình Lưu Minh Phủ Dung - 九日登望仙臺呈劉明府容</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%B4i-Th%E1%BB%B1/author-ZVNEdhHiylI-u5U8LhtREA">Thôi Thự</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/%C4%90%C3%A0m-Ch%C3%A2u-t%E1%BB%91ng-Vi-vi%C3%AAn-ngo%E1%BA%A1i-%C4%90i%E1%BB%81u-m%E1%BB%A5c-Thi%E1%BB%81u-Ch%C3%A2u/poem-XGlXFuExBf0pxI4DLXy2bA">Đàm Châu tống Vi viên ngoại Điều mục Thiều Châu - 潭州送韋員外迢牧韶州</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%C3%A0o-Ti%E1%BB%81m/%C4%90%C3%A0o-hoa-nguy%C3%AAn-k%C3%BD/poem-M9lemd9pQXAQfGzmHL9Ynw">Đào hoa nguyên ký - 桃花源記</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%C3%A0o-Ti%E1%BB%81m/author-y4iJ6v3mYp-Z_KEorcHd_g">Đào Tiềm</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-H%E1%BB%AFu-T%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng/%C4%90%E1%BB%81-D%E1%BB%A5c-Thu%C3%BD-s%C6%A1n/poem-ZDQbCPht2ab0hCbJDJCwWA">Đề Dục Thuý sơn - 題浴翆山</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-H%E1%BB%AFu-T%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng/author-SVL6yUvbtPvhDNgwRe-8Jw">Nguyễn Hữu Tường</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/%C4%90%E1%BB%81-ng%E1%BB%B1-b%C3%ACnh-ho%E1%BA%A1-%C4%91%E1%BB%93-k%E1%BB%B3-4-Gia-C%C3%A1t-t%E1%BA%BF-phong/poem-qxyzeEGnya51cNtE1mL3wQ">Đề ngự bình hoạ đồ kỳ 4 - Gia Cát tế phong - 題御屏畫圖其四－諸葛祭風</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/author-14GcnhLjD2ajP0MTgtX13Q">Ngô Thì Nhậm</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%A9a-H%E1%BB%93n/%C4%90%E1%BB%81-T%E1%BB%A9-H%E1%BA%A1o-mi%E1%BA%BFu/poem-3gdXc3XXr9kM3pEAjoO36g">Đề Tứ Hạo miếu - 題四皓廟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%A9a-H%E1%BB%93n/author-67u8r1Npo8IzUDBZnVHSFA">Hứa Hồn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-Bi%E1%BB%81n/T%E1%BA%A3-ho%C3%A0i-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-x2GPsNjj-8DNN4Uk_SdGAw">Tả hoài kỳ 1 - 寫懷其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-Bi%E1%BB%81n/author-qy2T-nw-JtHl_3EhgglyKg">Cao Biền</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Th%E1%BA%A3o-%C4%91%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng/poem-wwxs7iJe3IRK6mSsXfh_gQ">Thảo đường - 草堂</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Th%E1%BA%BF-Trinh/T%C3%B2ng-qu%C3%A2n-h%C3%A0nh/poem-Bv3fj5d7fpE70_uRe8vB7g">Tòng quân hành - 從軍行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Th%E1%BA%BF-Trinh/author-K5yGjv4-gkyzXKfuttJFiQ">Vương Thế Trinh</a>)<br></div>	</div>
